hs2_desc: Electric motors: of an output not exceeding 37.5W
Optical fibres, optical fibre bundles and cables: excluding those of heading no. 8544
Iron: non-alloy pig iron containing by weight 0.5% or less of phosphorus, in pigs, blocks or other primary forms
Ethylene polymers: in primary forms, polyethylene having a specific gravity of less than 0.94
Pearls: natural, whether or not worked or graded (but not strung, mounted or set), temporarily strung for the convenience of transport
Iron or steel: sheet piling, whether or not drilled, punched or made from assembled elements
